text: Ferenc Kemény (15 June 1922 - May 2002) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nyíregyháza
